# tooltip in username input

info_1: You don't need to to tell us your email address to use Picast. 
        Any user name you can remember will allow you to sign in.

info_2: Just keep in mind that if you choose to not use an email address, 
        we won't be able to send you a reset link should you forget your password.

info_3: If you change your mind you can always connect or remove your email address from your profile settings.
